  <thing id="cMBRecSrch" name="Resourceful Search" description="Once per day may attempt a Search check to find nonmagical, nor masterwork,  item of the player choice, for a maximum of 200gp value, without paying for it. The value, DC and time are written below.\n\nGP Value   Search DC   Search Time   Minimum City size\n&lt;20             10                   1d4x10 min      Hamlet\n21-50         15                   2d4x10 min      Small town\n51-100       20                   1d4 hours         Small City\n101-200     25                   2d4 hours         Metropolis" compset="ClSpecial" summary="Once per day, attempt Search check to fetch free item.">
