  <thing id="cChmAptFoc" name="Chameleon Aptitude Focus" description="Once per day (twice at lvl 5+) you can choose from one of five areas upon which to focus you ever-shifting talents.\n\n{i}Combat Focus:{/i}\nYou gain proficiency with all martial weapons and a +2 competence bonus to attack rolls, weapon damage rolls and fortitude saves (at 5th level the bonus is +4)\n\n{i}Stealth Focus:{/i}\nYou gain Trapfinding, uncanny dodge and a +2 competence bonus on Disable device, Hide, Move Silently, Open Lock, Search Checks and Reflex Saves (at 5th level, +4)\n\n{i}Wild Focus:{/i}\nYou gain Wild Empathy as a druid of your class level, Woodland stride, a +2 competence bonus on Climb, Handle Animal, Jump, Knowledge (nature), Survival Checks, and Fortitude Saves (at 5th level, +4).\n\n{i}Arcane Focus:{/i}\nYou gain the ability to prepare and cast a certain number of spells per day, using a spellbook as a wizard does. Your spell caster level is twice your class level. Spell characteristic is Intelligence.\nYou also gain a +2 competence bonus on Knowledge(Arcana) checks and a +2 bonus on Will saves (+4 at 5th lvl)\n{i}Divine Focus:{/i}\nYou gain the ability to prepare and cast a certain number of spells per day, just like a cleric does. Your spell caster level is twice your class level. Spell characteristic is Wisdom.\nYou also gain a +2 competence bonus on Knowledge(Religion) checks and a +2 bonus on Fortitude and Will saves (+4 at 5th lvl)" compset="ClSpecial">
    <usesource source="RoDestiny" parent="p35" name="Races of Destiny"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="cHelpChm"/>
    <tag group="ClSpecWhen" tag="1"/>
    <eval phase="UserPostLv" priority="1000"><![CDATA[~ Get the Chameleon level 
var level as number
var times as number
var bonus as number
level = hero.child[cHelpChm].field[cTotalLev].value

if (level >= 10) then
times = 3
bonus = 4
elseif (level >= 5) then
times = 2
bonus = 4
else
times = 1
bonus = 2
endif

field[xSumm].text = "Aptitude focus " & times & " times per day. Bonus to checks and save is +" & bonus & "."]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cChmBonFt" name="Chameleon Bonus Feat" description="You gain a bonus feat of your choice. You must meet the prerequisites for this feat, and you can change your choice at the start of each day." compset="ClSpecial">
