  <thing id="cChmmmc" name="Chameleon Mimic" description="Once per day (twice at lvl 6, thrice at lvl 9) you can mimic a class feature of other characters as for the list below:\n\n{i}Evasion:{/i}\nAs the rogue skill, can activate at the same time as a successful Reflex save, and lasts for 1 minute.\n\n{i}Rage:{/i}\nAs the barbarian skill, duration is your 1 + (newly improved) Constitution bonus  / rounds.\n\n{i}Smite:{/i}\nAs the paladin ability, but you can smite any enemy, your extra damage is equal to your class level.\n\n{i}Sneak Attack:{/i}\nAs the rogue ability, your extra damage is 1d6 for every three class level. Your rogue level is equal to your class level to defeat improved uncanny dodge.\n\n{i}Turn/Rebuke Undead:{/i}\nAs the cleric ability, your cleric level is equal to your class level." compset="ClSpecial">
    <usesource source="RoDestiny" parent="p35" name="Races of Destiny"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="cHelpChm"/>
