  <thing id="cOuCAvStrk" name="Outcast Champion Avenging Strike" description="You can attempt an avenging strike on an anemy who has dealt damage to an ally of yours within the last hour. The avenging strike must be dealt with a melee attack and has  a bonus to attack roll equal to your Charisma modifier, and deals 1d6 damage extra per outcast champion level. \nYou may use it a number of times per day equal to your charisma bonus." compset="ClSpecial">
