    </thing>
  <thing id="cOuCDsFry1" name="Outcast Champion Desperate Fury" description="Once per day, when you&apos;re reduce to fewer then one half your full normal hit points or when you&apos;re fatigued or exhausted, you can enter a state of desperate fury. While in this state, you gain a +2  morale bonus to Strength, Dexterity and Constitution. This state lasts for 3 rounds + 1 round per point of your (newly improved) Con bonus.\n\nAt 5th lvl, you become able to share the effect of your desperate fury with allies within 30 ft who can see you." compset="ClSpecial">
