  <thing id="cUrSCityR1" name="City Ramparts 1/day" description="Once per day (twice at 5th, thrice at 9th) you get a +4 Con Bonus, +2 bonus on Will Saves, and DR 5/adamantine. This effect lasts for 1 round per point of (adjusted) Constitution modifier.\n\nIf you are in a city the duration increases as noted below:\nSmall city - 3+Con mod\nLarge city - 5+Con mod\nMetropolis- 10+Con mod" compset="ClSpecial">
